&lt;p&gt;Gyffin Practice Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen within Gyffin Surgery in Conwy for a part time Practice Nurse working 35.25 hours per week over 5 days (days to be confirmed), working with an enthusiastic team just outside Conwy Castle, this renovated Chapel is situated on the Woodlands in Conwy. The Practice is a Health Board run Practice with approximately 4,000 patients with a full compliment of receptionists / administrators and nursing team. We currently have regular locum GPs working in Gyffin but have now received interest for salaried GP positions. This has a warm and friendly atmosphere where you will be made to feel at home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is essential for this post&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date - 16th November, 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information, please contact Debbie Searle, Practice Manager email debbie.searle@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
